title: Eye test is a must now Northwich children are back at school (Specsavers Optical Group ...
text: ( Source : Specsavers Optical Group Limited ) Now that a new school term in Northwich is underway, Specsavers is advising that it's an ideal time for children to have their eye health checked. One in four children have never had an eye test
